    "body": "Problem: Debouncing is common in both core and plugins.\r\n\r\nSolution: Add `vim.debounce(fn, wait, opts)` with lodash semantics.\r\n\r\nRef: https://www.npmjs.com/package/lodash.debounce\r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": null,
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
                    "href": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38999#discussion_r3072183598"
                },
                "pull_request": {
                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/38999"
                },
                "self": {
                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/comments/3072183598"
                }
            },
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'd either add docs for these directly here or link to the lodash.debounce docs",
            "commit_id": "e86c4c6b10ab37058639db421e38f23ea2312260",
            "created_at": "2026-04-13T09:55:43Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -1276,6 +1285,25 @@ vim.cmd({command})                                                 *vim.cmd()*\n     See also: ~\n       • |ex-cmd-index|\n \n+vim.debounce({fn}, {wait}, {opts})                            *vim.debounce()*\n+    Creates a debounced function that delays invoking `fn` until after `wait`\n+    milliseconds have elapsed since the last time the debounced function was\n+    invoked. >lua\n+        local d = vim.debounce(my_fn, 200, { leading = false, trailing = true })\n+        d('arg1', 'arg2')\n+        d:flush()           -- force immediate invocation\n+        d:cancel()          -- abandon pending invocation\n+        d:close()           -- cancel and release the underlying timer handle\n+<\n+\n+    Parameters: ~\n+      • {fn}    (`function`) Function to debounce.\n+      • {wait}  (`integer`) Delay in milliseconds.\n+      • {opts}  (`{ leading?: boolean, trailing?: boolean, maxwait?: integer }?`)",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38999#discussion_r3072183598",
